{"tid":88424,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"真係達哥兄弟最少起碼由Saints Row3到hitman 開始睇啦","createTime":"2017-01-20T15:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T16:16:37.000Z","uid":4352,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d125b9e6bd79e0c688dcce972d3fcf4da1db7e","tid":88424,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"當時嘅達叔真係可以同大家有互動<br />\nChatroom 嘅留言真係有質素<br />\n例如有好故事分享<br />\n生活難題想達叔解答<br />\n點溝女都有（溝日本妹事件）<br />\n但達哥開始出名<br />\n睇達哥變成潮流就開始有班九唔搭八嘅人出現<br />\n繼而小學雞入侵成個Chatroom就係洗版<br />\n-6 369 轉game<br />\n近年Chatroom太廢達哥要自己讀新聞<br />\n搞到fifa時段變悶由互動變成聽電台<br />\n最期待達哥玩人中因為多劇情多小遊戲俾佢亂黎<br />\n點撚知勁多撚屌話多劇情叫轉game<br />\n明明達叔最正係亂配旁白<br />\n根本唔係達哥低質左係睇班人低質左<br />\nBack up佬事件已經知一班人<br />\n人話兄弟佢就兄弟根本佢地只係觀眾<br />\n無真心當達哥係兄弟"},{"pid":"7d465f18ab7b5d1ade5de8d8555280e8acf65e2a","tid":88424,"uid":21249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"hitman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾黑警報串 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a5017483fe0cf58c1ad645f41238bc3e4a848e","tid":88424,"uid":4352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hitman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾黑警報串 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年hitman卡足三日<br />\n睇到屌出聲係都要殺死所有人<br />\n掉個滅火筒當油筒射完唔爆<br />\n輸左從新再打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18560b9e6a6cc16aef0b512e0c450aa137bc1ac0","tid":88424,"uid":59221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"太耐之前我都唔記得由幾時睇<br />\n但好記得有一次佢唱皆大歡喜 笑到我仆街<br />\n<br />\n果陣把聲仲係好似劉以達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋果陣CHATROOM唔係好多人"},{"pid":"621a412b681aa3442ca96f8756ded643cf0919b0","tid":88424,"uid":36243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor